title: Gilbert Gottfried | Late Night Democratic Presidential Debate, Round Five
description:
Seth moderates another high-stakes debate between the 2020 Democratic presidential candidates.

Gilbert Gottfried talks about his podcast, working with Larry David on a show called Norman’s Corner and his attempt to get a VIP pass to Disneyland. He also takes a few more additional questions backstage at Studio 8G.
